<i>noun</i>: 황폐화 [황폐화/황페화], 황폐 [황폐/황페], 피폐 [피폐/피페], 파괴 [파ː괴/파ː궤] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>황폐화 [황폐화/황페화]</dt><br>
<dd>1. devastation; ruin</dd><br>
<dd>집, 땅, 숲 등을 돌보지 않고 그냥 두어 거칠어지고 못 쓰게 됨. 또는 그렇게 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which houses, land, a forest, etc., are left unattended, becoming forlorn and useless; or an act of making this happen.</dd><br>
<dd>2. devastation; ruin; impoverishment</dd><br>
<dd>정신이나 생활 등이 거칠어지고 메마르게 됨. 또는 그렇게 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one's mind or life becomes dull and barren; or an act of making this happen.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>황폐 [황폐/황페]</dt><br>
<dd>1. devastation; ruin</dd><br>
<dd>집, 땅, 숲 등이 거칠어져 못 쓰게 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which houses, land, a forest, etc., become forlorn and useless.</dd><br>
<dd>2. devastation; ruin; impoverishment</dd><br>
<dd>정신이나 생활 등이 거칠어지고 메말라 감.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one's mind or life becomes dull and barren.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>피폐 [피폐/피페]</dt><br>
<dd>exhaustion; devastation</dd><br>
<dd>지치고 힘이 약해짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of becoming exhausted and weakened.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>파괴 [파ː괴/파ː궤]</dt><br>
<dd>1. destruction; devastation</dd><br>
<dd>때려 부수거나 깨뜨려 무너뜨림.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of smashing or breaking something into pieces to bring it down.</dd><br>
<dd>2. destruction; subversion; disruption</dd><br>
<dd>조직, 질서, 관계 등을 깨뜨려 무너뜨림.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of disrupting order, a relationship, etc., or dismantling an organization to ruin it completely.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>